# Optional. Reuse the same testnet account across runs.
# If unset, a throwaway testnet account is generated each run (printed to stdout).
# STELLAR_SECRET=S...

# Optional. How many times to poll transaction status (5s apart) before exiting.
# Default 120 (~10 minutes). Set to 1 for a quick smoke test.
# POLL_LIMIT=120

# ── Legacy app only (src/proxy.ts / the Vercel co-sign function) ──
# The LEGACY MoneyGram sandbox (extstellar.moneygram.com) requires SEP-10
# client_domain, so the backend co-signs the challenge with your signing key.
# This secret stays server-side — NEVER commit it, NEVER ship it to the browser.
# It must be the secret of the SIGNING_KEY published in your client_domain's
# stellar.toml (/.well-known/stellar.toml).
# CLIENT_DOMAIN_SIGNING_SECRET=S...
# CLIENT_DOMAIN=kaankacar.github.io
# MG_HOME=extstellar.moneygram.com
# MG_AUTH=https://extstellar.moneygram.com/stellaradapterservice/auth
# PORT=8765
